data.description: Check out this AMAZING home in one of the most sought after locations in Tampa Bay - Gulfport!  This 3/2,1 car garage, POOL home has SOLAR Panels that are paid off (original cost was over $30,000) and has saved the owner about $300-$400 a month since it has been installed!  NOT IN A FLOOD ZONE!  You'll love the RENOVATED KITCHEN, TILED FLOORS THROUGHOUT, MASTER CLOSET SPACE AND POOL AREA as well as the AMAZING LOCATION just a couple blocks from the Bay!  As you enter the home you'll love the OPEN LAYOUT of the home with views thru the home straight to the back yard pool area!  Immediately inside you'll be impressed by the large living room area with additional flex/sitting space off to the side.  There are endless uses for it... reading area, breakfast nook, office area, etc.  The entire house boasts tile - NO CARPET.   The kitchen is BEAUTIFUL and has TONS of counter space.  It has been renovated with tons of BEAUTIFUL GRANITE COUNTERTOP space and MODERN ELEGANT cabinets.  It also showcases TOP OF THE LINE NEWER STAINLESS STELL APPLIANCES!  You'll love the massive amounts of cabinet space and the built in pantry too.  As you proceed through the kitchen you will find the most inviting room of the house... the Great Room!  It is a wonderful place to RELAX and offers views of the back yard, screened in pool and lanai.  You'll love that there is plenty of space to sit and entertain with family and friends or just relax and watch some tv.    Even though this home is older - the design is pretty AMAZING!  The Master bedroom closet is H-U-G-E and offers so much more space than you could imagine!  You'll love the changing room area with room for a nice wardrobe or closet dresser if you like.  Seriously, this area is SPACIOUS!  The roomy feel doesn't stop here either... the Master Bathroom has been renovated and upgraded and offers plenty of space for the morning and evening routines for 2 people!  This home already offers so much inside but there is more!  The SCREENED IN POOL is the perfect place to host backyard parties and gatherings or to simply relax!  Enjoy the Florida lifestyle to its fullest anytime you like right in your own backyard!  You will appreciate the HUGE FENCED IN YARD not seen often in Gulfport.  So much space to do what you want with!  You will ABSOLUTELY LOVE this AMAZING LOCATION with all that Gulfport has to offer!  Ideally situation only a few blocks to the bay here are just a few of the POPULAR destinations that are must mere minutes away: Gulfport's Art District for First Friday's Art Walk each month (7 min bike ride), tons of restaurants and cafes within walking distance, St Pete Beach (8 min), Stetson University (3 min), Eckerd College (10 min), Pasadena Golf & Yacht Club (3 min), Maximo Boat Ramp (free boat launch) (11 min)... AND SO MUCH MORE!  Check out this house soon!  Interest rates just dropped in the past week and it is a great time to get an AMAZING house in Gulfport!
